__e: Well, perhaps this isn't going to be such a bad school after all. With you and Becky here.
But I hardly like to trouble him when I know that Becky will be on her way before too long.
Keith gets two, Becky gets one, you get one, I get four.
Every time I go home to Becky and those girls, I think this is it.
Oh, and please make sure your parents don't flake on the auction items they promised they'd bring. Thank you, Mary.
